## SEO & Monetization
1. **Unique Title**: `[Topic] - [Value Prop] | [Brand Name]`
2. **Meta Description**: Compelling, keyword-rich summary (150-160 chars).
3. **Canonical Tag**: Self-referencing canonical link pointing to `https://domain.com/[slug]/`.
4. **Semantic HTML**: Use `<header>`, `<main>`, `<article>`, `<footer>`.
5. **Ad Placeholders**: Always reserve space for ads (Top 728x90, Sidebar 300x600).
